<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        main {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto; 
        }
        footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05); 
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
<header>
  <nav class="h-24 border-gray-200 bg-sky-600">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between mx-auto p-7">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center space-x-3 rtl:space-x-reverse">
        <span class="self-center text-3xl font-semibold whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">Sportopia</span>
      </a>
      <button data-collapse-toggle="navbar-solid-bg" type="button" class="inline-flex items-center p-2 w-10 h-10 justify-center text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg md:hidden hover:bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:focus:ring-gray-600" aria-controls="navbar-solid-bg" aria-expanded="false">
        <span class="sr-only">Open main menu</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 17 14">
          <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M1 1h15M1 7h15M1 13h15"/>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <div class="hidden w-full md:block md:w-auto" id="navbar-solid-bg">
        <ul class="flex flex-col font-medium mt-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 md:space-x-8 rtl:space-x-reverse md:flex-row md:mt-0 md:border-0 md:bg-transparent dark:bg-gray-800 md:dark:bg-transparent dark:border-gray-700">
          <li>
            <a href="/" class="block py-2 px-3 text-2xl md:p-0 text-white bg-blue-700 rounded md:bg-transparent md:text-white md:dark:text-white dark:bg-blue-600 md:dark:bg-transparent hover:text-white hover:bg-blue-800 md:hover:bg-transparent md:border-0 md:hover:text-white dark:hover:text-white md:dark:hover:bg-transparent">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/about" class="block py-2 text-2xl px-3 md:p-0 text-gray-900 rounded text-white">About</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#features" class="block py-2 text-2xl px-3 md:p-0 text-gray-900 rounded text-white">Features</a>
          </li>
          <% if (user) { %>
            <li>
              <a href="/logout" class="block py-2 text-2xl px-3 md:p-0 text-gray-900 rounded text-white">Logout</a>
            </li>
          <% } else { %>
            <li>
              <a href="/login" class="block py-2 text-2xl px-3 md:p-0 text-gray-900 rounded text-white">Login/Register</a>
            </li>
          <% } %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto p-4">
    <p class="mt-2 text-3xl text-center pt-14">Plan and organize sports events...</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-3xl text-center pt-2">with Sportopia</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-center pt-4">Join today to create, schedule, and participate in sports events.</p>

    <section id="features" class="mt-12 mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center mb-8">Key Features</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-between card">
          <div>
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-600 mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3M16 7V3M3 8h18M4 12h16m-1 8h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5H9v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5m10 0h2"></path>
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Schedule Games</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Effortlessly schedule upcoming games and events with our intuitive scheduling tools.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-between card">
          <div>
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600 mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 20h10m-5-16a2 2 0 110 4 2 2 0 010-4zM4 15a4 4 0 014-4h8a4 4 0 014 4v1H4v-1z"></path>
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Manage Teams</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Create and manage teams effortlessly, assign roles, and track team performance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-between card">
          <div>
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-600 mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 17a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM6.343 9.657a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM15.657 9.657a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM6.343 14.343a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM15.657 14.343a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"></path>
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Track Statistics</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Monitor detailed statistics and performance metrics for teams and individual players.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-between card">
          <div>
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-yellow-600 mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 11l7 7 7-7M3 5h18"></path>
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Rankings and Leaderboards</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Stay updated with the latest rankings and leaderboards for various sports events.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-between card">
          <div>
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-red-600 mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h10M7 11h10m-5 4h5M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Mobile Access</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Access all features on the go with our mobile-friendly platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="testimonials" class="mt-12 mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center mb-8">Testimonials</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-between card">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9V7a4 4 0 018 0v2m0 4v2m0 3h0a2 2 0 01-2 2h-4a2 2 0 01-2-2h0"></path></svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold ml-2">John Doe</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">"Sportopia helped us seamlessly manage our sports events, making scheduling and team management a breeze!"</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-between card">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9V7a4 4 0 018 0v2m0 4v2m0 3h0a2 2 0 01-2 2h-4a2 2 0 01-2-2h0"></path></svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold ml-2">Jane Smith</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">"I love how Sportopia allows us to track detailed statistics and keep our teams organized effectively."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-between card">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9V7a4 4 0 018 0v2m0 4v2m0 3h0a2 2 0 01-2 2h-4a2 2 0 01-2-2h0"></path></svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold ml-2">Michael Johnson</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">"Sportopia's mobile access makes it easy for me to manage games and teams from anywhere, anytime."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>

<footer class="bg-emerald-700">
  <div class="w-full mx-auto max-w-screen-xl p-4 md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between">
    <span class="text-2xl text-white sm:text-center">© 2023 <a href="https://flowbite.com/" class="hover:underline text-white">Sportopia™</a>. All Rights Reserved.
    </span>
    <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-white dark:text-gray-400 sm:mt-0">
      <li>
        <a href="/about" class="hover:underline text-xl me-4 md:me-6 text-white">About</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/privacy-policy" class="hover:underline text-xl me-4 md:me-6 text-white">Privacy Policy</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/licensing" class="hover:underline me-4 text-xl md:me-6 text-white">Licensing</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/contact" class="hover:underline text-xl text-white">Contact</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
